04:49.000 --> 04:52.000
There are five stages in the chain of interrelations.

04:52.000 --> 04:58.000
The first stage is the so-called strategic analysis, when the company tries to understand

04:58.000 --> 05:03.000
what the configuration of forces in the external environment will look like in the near future,

05:03.000 --> 05:07.000
and tries to assess its own strengths and weaknesses at the moment,

05:07.000 --> 05:14.000
in order to apply all this to the next stage, stage number two,

05:14.000 --> 05:21.000
where the company formulates and evaluates alternatives for its own further development.

05:21.000 --> 05:25.000
There can be several, two, three, four.

05:25.000 --> 05:34.000
After evaluating and weighing the strategic alternatives, the company usually decides on one

05:34.000 --> 05:42.000
