16:48.000 --> 16:55.000
All companies can have their own specific nuances.

16:55.000 --> 17:03.000
In particular, the second projection can look different for different companies.

17:03.000 --> 17:10.000
As a rule, companies from all industries with any strategies need to build relations with their clients.

17:11.000 --> 17:15.000
And the client projection is available for the vast majority of companies.

17:15.000 --> 17:19.000
But some companies, within the framework of the second projection,

17:19.000 --> 17:26.000
