17:26.000 --> 17:35.000
For example, if a business company intends to build relations with officials, state bodies,

17:35.000 --> 17:40.000
and requires a lot of attention from top management,

17:40.000 --> 17:43.000
then within the framework of the second projection,

17:43.000 --> 17:46.000
goals can be set in relation to the state.

17:46.000 --> 17:54.000
There are companies whose business is based on very good relations with suppliers.

17:54.000 --> 18:02.000
And relations with suppliers can also be prescribed within the framework of the second projection.

18:03.000 --> 18:10.000
Or relations with partners, which are very important for the business,

18:10.000 --> 18:15.000
can also be prescribed in the second projection.

18:15.000 --> 18:18.000
Therefore, for some companies, this projection is not called a client and product,

18:18.000 --> 18:21.000
but a client and product of the state.

18:21.000 --> 18:23.000
Or a client and product of a supplier.

18:23.000 --> 18:28.000
In fact, the second projection is intended to list all those

18:28.000 --> 18:33.000
with whom we in our business, in our industry, should build relations to earn some money.

18:33.000 --> 18:37.000
The third projection is business processes.

18:37.000 --> 18:44.000
The entire chain of processes of the company is considered here, in a large cage, as a rule.

18:44.000 --> 18:46.000
But the entire chain of processes.

18:46.000 --> 18:50.000
And at the fourth stage, we already talked about what people we need

18:50.000 --> 18:56.000
to achieve the goals in the above projections,

18:56.000 --> 18:58.000
