18:58.000 --> 19:03.000
Infrastructure is usually called software products, equipment, buildings,

19:03.000 --> 19:07.000
maybe transport, which people need,

19:07.000 --> 19:11.000
personnel need to perform processes normally.

19:11.000 --> 19:17.000
And the connection between these four projections is quite logical.

19:17.000 --> 19:21.000
