22:18.000 --> 22:22.000
we compare it with the amount of capital invested in the business,

22:22.000 --> 22:25.000
and looking at the value of this parameter,

22:25.000 --> 22:31.000
we understand how effective the dollars, euros or rubles invested in our business are.

22:31.000 --> 22:42.000
And finally, another category in the finance projection is the business value.

22:42.000 --> 22:53.000
This category is of interest only to those businessmen who want to sell,

22:53.000 --> 22:59.000
who grow their business for sale.

22:59.000 --> 23:05.000
The business value is the same as the well-being of shareholders

23:05.000 --> 23:08.000
