23:08.000 --> 23:12.000
As a rule, shareholders want to become richer,

23:12.000 --> 23:16.000
and therefore, the goals related to the business value

23:16.000 --> 23:19.000
can be of absolutely all companies, public and not,

23:19.000 --> 23:23.000
focused on sales and not focused on sales.

