At the structural level, we observe the same four projections.

01:36:13.000 --> 01:36:15.000
The financial projection.

01:36:15.000 --> 01:36:21.000
There are structural units in which only expenses arise, they must fit into the budget.

01:36:21.000 --> 01:36:24.000
The second projection is the clients.

01:36:24.000 --> 01:36:32.000
The units at the front will have external clients and internal colleagues, with whom you also need to build relations.

01:36:32.000 --> 01:36:34.000
The second projection is the clients.

01:36:34.000 --> 01:36:43.000
The units at the front will have external clients and internal colleagues, with whom you also need to build relations.

01:36:43.000 --> 01:36:56.000
The units at the rear, the service services, will have internal clients, who must be serviced on time and efficiently.

01:36:57.000 --> 01:37:02.000
Everyone has a projection of processes and personnel.

